INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `is_offer`, `video`, `ico`, `short_des`, `description`, `tag`, `cat_id`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(41, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing-2', '1666435192.png', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\">Digital Marketing</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is the marketing of products or services using digital technologies, mainly on the Internet, but also including mobile phones, display advertising, and any other digital medium.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is an umbrella term for all of your online marketing efforts. Businesses leverage digital channels such as Google search, social media, email, and their websites to connect with their current and prospective customers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With how accessible the internet is today, would you believe me if I told you the number of people who go online every day is still increasing? It is! In fact, “According to Internetlivestats, over 4 billion people are active internet users”. That’s a huge portion of the world’s population!</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With so many people using the internet every day, it’s no surprise that digital marketing has become a hot topic. After all, it’s an effective way to reach your target market without spending a lot of money.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is digital marketing?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is the process of using the internet and digital devices to reach and engage customers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It encompasses all marketing activities that use digital technologies. This includes things like search engine optimization (SEO), content marketing, social media marketing, email marketing, and more.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is a huge topic. And it can be overwhelming to try to keep up with all the latest trends and changes. But don’t worry, that’s what we’re here for. In this article, we’ll give you a high-level overview of digital marketing and some of the most important things to keep in mind.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Why is digital marketing important?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(1