(47, 'Graphics Design', 'graphics-design-2', '1666435968.jpg', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 2.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Branding</span></h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In marketing, branding is the use of a name, term, design, symbol, or other feature to identify a product or service and distinguish it from those of other producers. The key components of a brand include the brand name, brand logo, brand identity, and brand messaging.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">The importance of Branding&nbsp;</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Branding is an important part of any business, large or small. A strong brand can help a company to stand out in a crowded marketplace, build customer trust and loyalty, and increase its value. Branding can also be a major liability if not done correctly, so it is important to understand the process and how to do it correctly.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The process of branding starts with research to understand the customer, the competition, and the company’s strengths and weaknesses. This is followed by the development of a brand strategy, which includes the selection of a brand name, logo, and identity. The brand strategy is then implemented through marketing communications, such as advertising, public relations, and social media.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When done correctly, branding can be a powerful tool for any business. Understanding the process and how to do it correctly is essential for any company looking to create a strong brand.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">There are many benefits to branding, including the ability to:</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create customer loyalty: Customers who are loyal to a brand are more likely to continue buying from that brand in the future, even when other options are available.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"2\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increase customer awareness: A strong brand will be recognizable and top of mind for potential customers, making them more likely to think of your business when they need your products or services.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"3\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Attract new customers: A well-known brand can attract new customers who may not have considered your business before.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"4\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build trust: Customers who trust a brand are more likely to do business with that brand and recommend it to others.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"5\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">differentiate from competitors: A strong brand can help your business stand out from the competition and be more easily remembered by potential customers.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"6\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Command higher prices: Customers who are loyal to a brand are often willing to pay more for products or services from that brand, due to the perceived value of the brand.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"7\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create shareholder value: A strong brand can increase the value of a company, making it more attractive to potential investors.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"8\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generate positive word-of-mouth: Satisfied customers who feel positively about a brand are more likely to tell others about their good experiences, which can lead to even more customers.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"9\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increase employee morale: Employees who are proud to work for a strong brand are more likely to be engaged and motivated, leading to a higher level of productivity.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"10\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create a lasting impression: A strong brand can leave a lasting impression on customers and help your business be remembered long after they’ve made a purchase.</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A strong brand can be a major asset to a company, making it more valuable and helping it to stand out in a crowded marketplace. Branding can also be a major liability if not done correctly, resulting in a loss of customer trust and loyalty.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When done correctly, branding can help a company to build customer trust and loyalty, differentiate itself from its competitors, and increase its value. Branding can also be used to create an emotional connection with customers, making them more likely to be loyal and engaged.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Process of Branding&nbsp;</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This starts with research to understand the customer, the competition, and the company’s strengths and weaknesses. This is followed by the development of a brand strategy, which includes the selection of a brand name, logo, and identity. The brand strategy is then implemented through marketing communications, such as advertising, public relations, and social media.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The process of branding starts with research to understand the customer, the competition, and the company’s strengths and weaknesses. This is followed by the development of a brand strategy, which includes the selection of a brand name, logo, and identity. The brand strategy is then implemented through marketing communications, such as advertising, public relations, and social media.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A strong brand is built over time through a consistent and cohesive application of the brand strategy. It takes time and effort to build a strong brand, but the payoff can be significant. A strong brand can create customer loyalty, increase customer lifetime value, and help a company to weather difficult times.</span></p>', 'Digital Marketing,                                         App Design & Development,                                         Software', 10, 1, '2022-10-22 04:50:57', '2022-10-22 04:52:49');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `is_offer`, `video`, `ico`, `short_des`, `description`, `tag`, `cat_id`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(48, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing-2', '1666435192.png', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\">Digital Marketing</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is the marketing of products or services using digital technologies, mainly on the Internet, but also including mobile phones, display advertising, and any other digital medium.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is an umbrella term for all of your online marketing efforts. Businesses leverage digital channels such as Google search, social media, email, and their websites to connect with their current and prospective customers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With how accessible the internet is today, would you believe me if I told you the number of people who go online every day is still increasing? It is! In fact, “According to Internetlivestats, over 4 billion people are active internet users”. That’s a huge portion of the world’s population!</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With so many people using the internet every day, it’s no surprise that digital marketing has become a hot topic. After all, it’s an effective way to reach your target market without spending a lot of money.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is digital marketing?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is the process of using the internet and digital devices to reach and engage customers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It encompasses all marketing activities that use digital technologies. This includes things like search engine optimization (SEO), content marketing, social media marketing, email marketing, and more.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is a huge topic. And it can be overwhelming to try to keep up with all the latest trends and changes. But don’t worry, that’s what we’re here for. In this article, we’ll give you a high-level overview of digital marketing and some of the most important things to keep in mind.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Why is digital marketing important?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is important because it allows businesses to reach a larger audience with less money.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s also important because it’s one of the most effective ways to connect with your target market.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Think about it this way…</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to reach people who are