sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A strong brand is built over time through a consistent and cohesive application of the brand strategy. It takes time and effort to build a strong brand, but the payoff can be significant. A strong brand can create customer loyalty, increase customer lifetime value, and help a company to weather difficult times.</span></p>', 'Digital Marketing,                                         App Design & Development,                                         Software', 10, 1, '2022-10-22 04:50:57', '2022-10-22 04:52:49');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `is_offer`, `video`, `ico`, `short_des`, `description`, `tag`, `cat_id`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(56, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing-2', '1666435192.png', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\">Digital Marketing</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is the marketing of products or services using digital technologies, mainly on the Internet, but also including mobile phones, display advertising, and any other digital medium.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is an umbrella term for all of your online marketing efforts. Businesses leverage digital channels such as Google search, social media, email, and their websites to connect with their current and prospective customers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With how accessible the internet is today, would you believe me if I told you the number of people who go online every day is still increasing? It is! In fact, “According to Internetlivestats, over 4 billion people are active internet users”. That’s a huge portion of the world’s population!</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With so many people using the internet every day, it’s no surprise that digital marketing has become a hot topic. After all, it’s an effective way to reach your target market without spending a lot of money.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is digital marketing?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is the process of using the internet and digital devices to reach and engage customers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It encompasses all marketing activities that use digital technologies. This includes things like search engine optimization (SEO), content marketing, social media marketing, email marketing, and more.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is a huge topic. And it can be overwhelming to try to keep up with all the latest trends and changes. But don’t worry, that’s what we’re here for. In this article, we’ll give you a high-level overview of digital marketing and some of the most important things to keep in mind.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Why is digital marketing important?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital marketing is important because it allows businesses to reach a larger audience with less money.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s also important because it’s one of the most effective ways to connect with your target market.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Think about it this way…</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to reach people who are interested in what you do, where are they most likely to be? Online!</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">That’s why digital marketing is so important. It’s the most efficient and effective way to reach your target market.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What are the benefits of digital marketing?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are many benefits of digital marketing. Some benefits of digital marketing include:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increased visibility: Digital marketing techniques can help increase the visibility of your brand or product.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">More engaging content: Digital marketing allows you to create more engaging and interesting content than traditional marketing techniques.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Greater reach: Digital marketing can help you reach a larger audience more easily than traditional marketing techniques.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">More engaging customers: Digital marketing can help you engage with your customers more effectively than traditional marketing techniques.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What are the goals of digital marketing?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The goals of digital marketing are to increase brand awareness, drive traffic to company websites, and generate leads and sales.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It depends on the size and type of business. But in general, the goals of digital marketing can be broken down into the following categories:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increase website traffic</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"2\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generate leads and sales</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"3\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increase brand awareness and credibility</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"4\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build relationships with customers and prospects</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"5\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stay ahead of your competition</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What are the different types of digital marketing?</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are many different types of digital marketing.Most common types of digital marketing are email marketing, social media marketing, content marketing, pay-per-click advertising, and search engine optimization.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are some of the most common ones:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Search engine optimization (SEO)</span></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(103, 121, 147); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"2\" style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: 