(20, 'SEO', 'Search Engine Optimization', 'seo', '1667369423.png', NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Chivo, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">Search engine optimization is the most potential marketing platform in digital marketing. Because people go to a search engine with the intention of buying a product or</span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Chivo, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Chivo, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\">service. So if a company can rank its website it will probably get more sales and revenue. In order to make your website more visible to the audience, you have to know about SEO. Because it’s a very long process and there are many competitors in SEO. To compete with them you should make your site updated, unique, and quality content, and keyword research properly.</span><br></p>', 'Digital Marketing,                                         Graphic Design,                                         Web Design & Development,                                         App Design & Development,                                         Software', 19, 1, '2022-11-02 00:10:23', '2022-11-02 00:10:23'),
